@startuml sequence_csv2graph_build
title Sequence Diagram - Luồng build CSV2Graph

autonumber
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #334155
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #0F766E
skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #ECFDF5

actor "Người dùng" as User
boundary "Frontend\nCsvUploadPanel" as FE
control "Backend\nCsv2GraphController" as Controller
control "Csv2GraphService" as Csv2Graph
control "SchemaLlmService" as SchemaLlm
control "FeatureService" as Feature
control "StarGraphService" as StarGraph
control "CsvOutputService" as CsvOutput
control "Neo4jIngestService" as Ingest
database "Neo4j" as Neo4j
collections "Metadata Cache\n_latest_[database].json" as Meta
actor "CSV2Graph LLM\n/ Colab API" as Llm

User -> FE: Chọn CSV
FE -> Controller: POST /csv2graph/suggest-transaction-id
Controller -> SchemaLlm: suggestTransactionId(headers, samples)
SchemaLlm -> Llm: Gửi headers + sample values
Llm --> SchemaLlm: Gợi ý transaction_id
Controller --> FE: suggestion + uniqueCols

User -> FE: Chọn Transaction ID\nvà bấm Build Graph
FE -> Controller: POST /csv2graph/run\ntrainMode=false, pretrainedMode=false
Controller -> Csv2Graph: run(file, dto)
Csv2Graph -> Meta: loadLatest(database)
Meta --> Csv2Graph: Không có metadata hoặc DB rỗng

Csv2Graph -> CsvOutput: Lưu input CSV + tạo jobDir
Csv2Graph -> Csv2Graph: Parse CSV
Csv2Graph -> SchemaLlm: classify(headers, samples)
SchemaLlm -> Llm: Suy luận schema CSV
Llm --> SchemaLlm: node_id, relation_cols, feature_cols
SchemaLlm --> Csv2Graph: FullSchema

Csv2Graph -> Feature: Chuẩn hóa feature
Feature --> Csv2Graph: rawRows + encodedRows
Csv2Graph -> StarGraph: Build star graph edges
StarGraph --> Csv2Graph: edges
Csv2Graph -> CsvOutput: Ghi nodes.csv, edges.csv, schema.json

note over Csv2Graph
  Không train và không demo:
  không cần targetLabel,
  không tạo data.pt.
end note

Csv2Graph -> Ingest: ingest(rawRows, edges, CREATE mode)
Ingest -> Neo4j: CREATE nodes + relationships
Neo4j --> Ingest: Số nodes/relationships
Ingest --> Csv2Graph: ingested stats

Csv2Graph -> Meta: saveLatest(database, metadata)
Csv2Graph --> Controller: Csv2GraphRunResponse
Controller --> FE: Build success
FE --> User: Toast + cập nhật graph preview

@enduml
